                        text="&lt;p>AbbVie PRIDE’s mission is to foster a safe and inclusive environment for our current and future LGBTQ+ colleagues.&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>Our primary objectives are to make a remarkable impact for patients and customers by:&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xa; &lt;li>Encouraging all employees to bring their whole, authentic selves to work, unlocking the exponential potential found in each person.&lt;/li>&#xa; &lt;li>Fostering connectivity and internal sense of community.&amp;amp;nbsp;&lt;/li>&#xa; &lt;li>Supporting the LGBTQ+ community in visible ways.&lt;/li>&#xa; &lt;li>Furthering education around LGBTQ+ issues to raise awareness and heighten sensitivity.&amp;amp;nbsp;&amp;amp;nbsp;&lt;/li>&#xa;&lt;/ul>"/>
